## ‚öôÔ∏è System Requirements
- **OS**: 64-bit Windows 10 / Windows 11
- **Python**: 3.7+ (64-bit)
- **Disk Space**: ‚â•10MB (package + built-in DLL)
- **RAM**: Minimal (depends on dataset size‚Äîworks with 4GB+ RAM)

